OKMARK左唔知睇唔睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我睇小說介紹 似係條友鳩遊輕鬆小品?<br />\n<br />\n定係冒險 熱血打鬥個類?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用我之前覆過人段野覆你<br />\n<br />\n主角奇諾去每個國家遊歷，<br />\n而每個國家有唔同背後故事同問題但主角盡量唔會插手干預，例如大人之國、和平之國、xxx之國<br />\n而嗰啲問題映射緊現實社會唔同問題<br />\n<br />\n一個章節一個故事，有時書頭書尾會分a、b章玩吓倒敘法講一個故事<br />\n<br />\n每個故事睇完你都會有啲反思同啟發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n力推呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小説我就覺幾精彩，動畫就睇佢演繹成點"},{"pid":"9655cbb9ef4183f7af51fc3e31a4b4d96e1c34c9","tid":326874,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母幾時有我出場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49056c29d32a0d7eca52e21c07296aeb9d612749","tid":326874,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"umaru<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484fa8d641d7b15555ebb69395a5af6772729d5d","tid":326874,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pop team epic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10月最強新番</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/utybi9zs\" dat